(1/n)  Suggestion for a new medical terminology for long-term health effects due to the #CovidVaccine.
In analogy to "long COVID" (= PASC, PACS) => https://t.co/4veASrsPEe

(3/n)  I suggest the following term for the post-accute effects:
- Post-acute sequelae of COVID-19 vaccination (PASCV), or
- Post-acute COVID-19 vaccination syndrome (PACVS)

I expect to see many cases of #PACVS in the near future.

#CovidVaccine #vaccineSideEffects
